## Request Parameters
<a name="API_waf_GetGeoMatchSet_RequestParameters"></a>

For information about the parameters that are common to all actions, see [Common Parameters](CommonParameters.md).

The request accepts the following data in JSON format.

 ** [GeoMatchSetId](#API_waf_GetGeoMatchSet_RequestSyntax) **   <a name="WAF-waf_GetGeoMatchSet-request-GeoMatchSetId"></a>
The `GeoMatchSetId` of the [GeoMatchSet](API_waf_GeoMatchSet.md) that you want to get. `GeoMatchSetId` is returned by [CreateGeoMatchSet](API_waf_CreateGeoMatchSet.md) and by [ListGeoMatchSets](API_waf_ListGeoMatchSets.md).  
Type: String  
Length Constraints: Minimum length of 1. Maximum length of 128.  
Pattern: `.*\S.*`   
Required: Yes

## Response Syntax
<a name="API_waf_GetGeoMatchSet_ResponseSyntax"></a>

{
   "GeoMatchSet": { 
